		<h2 class="font__title2">HTML Classes</h2>
		<h3 class="font__title3 heading__separator">Font Style Classes</h3>

		<h4 class="font__subheading"><code>.font__caption</code> Caption font style</h4>
		<p class="sp__0"><em>When to use?</em> Captions. Legal text. Use sparingly.</p>
		<brik-editor editable="true" live-preview="true">
			<brik-code lang="html">&lt;p class="font__caption">Caption: Regular 12sp&lt;/p></brik-code>
		</brik-editor>

		<h4 class="font__subheading"><code>.font__button</code> Button font style</h4>
